{"tid":101079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又一隻】派出所文職人員 團年飯後斬殺老婆","createTime":"2017-01-30T14:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T15:05:39.000Z","uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfca6ae14db4923e024d41af26dae936a6036417","tid":101079,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"【又一隻】派出所文職人員 團年飯後斬殺老婆<br />\n<br />\n甘肅慶陽市公安局職員今日證實，年三十晚(27日)派出所一名田姓文職人員涉嫌持刀殺害妻子，已被警方刑事拘留。考慮到迴避原則，案件已交由慶陽市合水縣公安局調查。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，慶陽市華池縣橋河中學語文教師王霞在家中遇害，王霞的父親王潤軍稱，殺害女兒就是其女婿。王潤軍指，女兒現年33歲，2015年1月結婚。婚後，兩人住在他家的老房子裏，曾因新房裝修資金問題發生過爭執，後來感情逐漸疏遠，女兒不想再與丈夫一起生活，年前還向當地法院提出離婚。<br />\n<br />\n王潤軍又指，事發當晚，在派出所值班的田姓女婿返回家中吃飯。飯前，兩人再次發生爭執。當晚10時左右，田男持刀將妻子斬傷，家人發現後立即將其送院急救，但延至翌日凌晨傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n女教師遭丈夫用刀刺死，右為王霞生前的舊照。(互聯網)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170130/large/1485778961_dabb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F1485778961_dabb.jpg&h=be4b8c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170130/56241940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170130%2F56241940&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=c91e521b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170130%2F56241940&h=d7e8101e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170130/56241940</a>"},{"pid":"6fbf8d670f6170167c3707735131da8fa9d0dd47","tid":101079,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4a7299e5e3be2b6032827f08cc3f89d9a5a8e3","tid":101079,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"槍斃咪兩隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}